OOC: Just thought I would add my two cents. I do agree that missiles
shouldnt be fired, but they do have a much more advanced technology than
we do, so we dont know for sure. I do know that a transformers body is
able to stabalize pressures, as they were doing it in a comic book
issue, but it is very energy costly, and as soon as their energy runs
out, they would begin to get crushed. That isnt the end all of the
discussion, just what I thought. Remember, the Autobots and Decepticons
were blasting missiles at each other underwater in two different
episodes (Atlantis Arise, The Ultimate Doom part 1), suggesting that
maybe their artilary can stand up to pressures.
